	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><strong>Action</strong> - 50 ft. Radius, 100 ft. Cylinder (Range 100 ft.) - 7th Level (Transmutation) - VS - Concentration (1 Minute)</p><br><p><br /></p><br><p><strong>[[/save DEX]]{Dexterity Save}</strong></p><br><p>Gravity reverses in a 50-foot-radius, 100-foot-high cylinder centered on a point within range. A creature automatically fails the Dexterity save if it cannot grab onto a fixed object.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> The creature or object is flung upward. If it strikes a solid surface (such as a ceiling), it takes normal fall damage from the collision. If no surface is struck, it remains suspended at the top of the area, oscillating slightly, for the duration.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> The creature manages to grab a fixed object and avoid being flung upward, though gravity in the area remains reversed.</p></li><li><p>When the spell ends, all affected creatures and objects fall back down.</p></li></ul>",
